	<h1 class="title">有意思的玩具不多了，你要不要来试试这些电动车？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/121376/small/121376.jpg?1434268095" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Nara Shin</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-06 08:04:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15696/medium/15696.jpg?1444055725" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="15696" data-title="《有意思的玩具不多了，你要不要来试试这些电动车？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/15696/medium/15696.jpg?1444055725" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/15696.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
